Ted Ings Presents FIXED OPS ROUNDTABLE: JUMANJI!, Virtual Event, Thursday, December 3, 2020

Ted Ings Presents: FIXED OPS ROUNDTABLE: JUMANJI! – The Virtual Event

Thursday, December 3, 2020, 9:00 AM EST

Complimentary General Admission

Join us for an interactive roundtable among industry peers, featuring an in-depth discussion of fixed ops strategies!

See our recent virtual event program (October 23, 2020): FixedOpsTireSummit.com

No Refunds on tickets or sponsorships – Tickets may be transferred to someone else.

The Agenda (All Times Eastern):

8:45 am – DOORS OPEN
9:00 am – EVENT BEGINS!
9:00 – 9:15 am – TED INGS, YOUR HOST; GENE GIRDLEY, EVENT PRODUCER; KARA DELAINE, HENSON BRAND DEALERSHIPS, CO-HOST; BEN PRICE, MASTER OF CEREMONIES; TULLY WILLIAMS, THE NIELLO COMPANY; GLENN LUNDY, #RISEANDGRIND; JOE ST JOHN, AUTO FI;- ROUNDTABLE KICK-OFF
9:15 – 9:30 am -JOE ST. JOHN, AUTO FI – GUEST SPEAKER

9:30 – 9:55 am – CHRIS SARACENO, VP/PARTNER, KELLY AUTOMOTIVE GROUP, AUTHOR – THEORY OF 5 – KEYNOTE SPEAKER (AM)

9:55 – 10:00 am -BREAK
10:00 – 10:30 am – TEAM VELOCITY PANEL DISCUSSION – PARTICIPANTS TO BE ANNOUNCED!
10:30 – 10:45 am – ROB LEARY, BG PRODUCTS
10:45 – 11:00 am – COURTNEY WHITE, DEALERWARE
11:00 – 11:05 am – BREAK
11:05 – 11:35 pm – “ACTIVE LEADERSHIP” PANEL DISCUSSION – JOHN FAIRCHILD, FAIRCHILD AUTOMOTIVE SOLUTIONS; ED ROBERTS, BOZARD FORD LINCOLN; SHON KINGREY, STEP ONE AUTOMOTIVE GROUP
11:35 – 11:50 – LES SILVER, DYNATRON SOFTWARE
11:50 – 12:05 – ANTHONY MONTEIRO, DRAIVER
12:05- 12:10 pm – BREAK

12:10 – 12:25 pm – OWEN MOON, FIXED OPS DIGITAL

12:25 – 12:40 pm – PRESENTATION
12:40 – 12:55 pm – PRESENTATION
12:55 – 1:00 pm – BREAK
1:05 – 1: 35 pm- PANEL DISCUSSION – PARTICIPANTS TO BE ANNOUNCED!
1:35 – 1:50 pm – KEN LOHR, BELLAVIA BLATT, PC
1:55- 2:00 pm – BREAK
2:00 – 2: 15 pm – FIXED OPS DIGITAL
2:15 – 2:45 pm – PANEL DISCUSSION – PARTICIPANTS TO BE ANNOUNCED!
2:45 – 3:00 pm – PRESENTATION
3:00 – 3:05 pm – BREAK

3:05 – 3:30 – ERICH GAIL, CEO, CARDINALE GROUP OF COMPANIES, CARDINALE AUTOMOTIVE GROUP – KEYNOTE SPEAKER (PM)

3:30 – 4:00 pm – PANEL DISCUSSION – PARTICIPANTS TO BE ANNOUNCED!
4:00 – 4:05 pm – BREAK
4:10 – 4:25 pm – PRESENTATION
4:25 – 4:40 pm – PRESENTATION
4:40 – 4:55 pm – PRESENTATION
4:55 – 5:00 pm – BREAK
5:00 – 5:30 pm -PANEL DISCUSSION – PARTICIPANTS TO BE ANNOUNCED!
5:30 – 5:45 pm – BEST PRACTICE AWARDS VOTING AND PRESENTATION
5:45 – 6:00 pm – Future Announcements: FIXED OPS ROUNDTABLE # 10 – “REV IT UP!” (FEBRUARY 9, 10 and 11, 2021)
6:00 pm – Adjorn
